data.description: VRM Sellers will entertain offers between $225,000 - $235,000. Welcome to 5182 Verbena Court W! This charming brick home is nestled on a generous half-acre lot. It boasts a cozy ambiance with new living room flooring and freshly painted interiors. This home offers a living room as well as family room, eat-in kitchen and dining space. The bathrooms feature new shower heads and the kitchen shines with painted cabinets and new hardware. The spacious primary bedroom offers access to the back porch. Stay comfortable year-round with the brand new HVAC system (2023). Tucked away in a tranquil cul-de-sac, this property also offers a spacious shed/workshop in the backyard. This home is close to shopping and schools. Septic tank was inspected in 2022. All pertinent information to be verified by the buyer. Come check out all this home has to offer today!
